Tree Data with Master Detail, Test IDs, Compact Column Headers, Grid Context in Integrated Charts, Accessibility Improvements.

## What's New

AG Grid {% migrationVersion() %} adds important new features – [Tree Data with Master Detail](./master-detail-other/#tree-data), [Test IDs](./testing/#test-ids), [Compact Column Headers](./column-groups/#hide-padded-header-rows), [Grid Context in Integrated Charts](./integrated-charts-customisation/#accessing-grid-context-in-formatters), Accessibility Improvements, as described in the [release post](https://blog.ag-grid.com/whats-new-in-ag-grid-34-1/).

These improvements involve no breaking changes as listed below.

